{"parentUuid":"88568787-daa6-46b6-bc35-bd5cd8a88c75","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"88b5953e-fd6d-4fc6-b6e7-3e3f85222ad1","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DthjmNWM7LSKPXFuGaiqP5","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /Users/SteffenPlunder/Documents/Workspace/ping-pong/game-of-life.html"}]},"uuid":"8a167ed8-21ab-49d7-996b-dcee7cc4c529","timestamp":"2026-04-17T08:27:24.752Z","toolUseResult":{"type":"create","filePath":"/Users/SteffenPlunder/Documents/Workspace/ping-pong/game-of-life.html","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<title>Conway's Game of Life</title>\n<style>\n  body {\n    margin: 0;\n    min-height: 100vh;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    background: #0f1117;\n    color: #e6e8ef;\n    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif;\n    gap: 16px;\n    padding: 20px;\n  }\n  h1 { margin: 0; font-weight: 500; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }\n  canvas {\n    background: #1a1d26;\n    border: 1px solid #2a2e3a;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    cursor: crosshair;\n  }\n  .controls { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }\n  button {\n    background: #2a2e3a; color: #e6e8ef; border: 1px solid #3a3f4d;\n    padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 14px;\n    transition: background 0.15s;\n  }\n  button:hover { background: #353a48; }\n  button.primary { background: #4a7eff; border-color: #4a7eff; }\n  button.primary:hover { background: #3a6eee; }\n  label { font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.8; }\n  input[type=\"range\"] { vertical-align: middle; }\n  .stats { font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.6; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>Conway's Game of Life</h1>\n  <canvas id=\"board\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\"></canvas>\n  <div class=\"controls\">\n    <button id=\"toggle\" class=\"primary\">Start</button>\n    <button id=\"step\">Step</button>\n    <button id=\"clear\">Clear</button>\n    <button id=\"random\">Random</button>\n    <label>Speed: <input id=\"speed\" type=\"range\" min=\"1\" max=\"60\" value=\"15\"></label>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"stats\">\n    Generation: <span id=\"gen\">0</span> · Alive: <span id=\"alive\">0</span> · Click/drag to draw\n  </div>\n\n<script>\n(() => {\n  const CELL = 8;\n  const canvas = document.getElementById('board');\n  const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');\n  const cols = canvas.width / CELL;\n  const rows = canvas.height / CELL;\n\n  let grid = new Uint8Array(cols * rows);\n  let next = new Uint8Array(cols * rows);\n  let running = false;\n  let generation = 0;\n  let lastTick = 0;\n  let fps = 15;\n\n  const idx = (x, y) => y * cols + x;\n\n  function draw() {\n    ctx.fillStyle = '#1a1d26';\n    ctx.fillRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);\n    ctx.fillStyle = '#6cf0a8';\n    let alive = 0;\n    for (let y = 0; y < rows; y++) {\n      for (let x = 0; x < cols; x++) {\n        if (grid[idx(x, y)]) {\n          ctx.fillRect(x * CELL, y * CELL, CELL - 1, CELL - 1);\n          alive++;\n        }\n      }\n    }\n    document.getElementById('alive').textContent = alive;\n    document.getElementById('gen').textContent = generation;\n  }\n\n  function step() {\n    for (let y = 0; y < rows; y++) {\n      for (let x = 0; x < cols; x++) {\n        let n = 0;\n        for (let dy = -1; dy <= 1; dy++) {\n          for (let dx = -1; dx <= 1; dx++) {\n            if (dx === 0 && dy === 0) continue;\n            const nx = (x + dx + cols) % cols;\n            const ny = (y + dy + rows) % rows;\n            n += grid[idx(nx, ny)];\n          }\n        }\n        const alive = grid[idx(x, y)];\n        next[idx(x, y)] = (alive && (n === 2 || n === 3)) || (!alive && n === 3) ? 1 : 0;\n      }\n    }\n    [grid, next] = [next, grid];\n    generation++;\n  }\n\n  function loop(ts) {\n    if (running && ts - lastTick >= 1000 / fps) {\n      step();\n      draw();\n      lastTick = ts;\n    }\n    requestAnimationFrame(loop);\n  }\n\n  // --- Drawing with mouse ---\n  let drawing = false;\n  let drawValue = 1;\n  function cellFromEvent(e) {\n    const r = canvas.getBoundingClientRect();\n    const x = Math.floor((e.clientX - r.left) * (canvas.width / r.width) / CELL);\n    const y = Math.floor((e.clientY - r.top) * (canvas.height / r.height) / CELL);\n    return { x, y };\n  }\n  canvas.addEventListener('mousedown', e => {\n    drawing = true;\n    const { x, y } = cellFromEvent(e);\n    if (x < 0 || x >= cols || y < 0 || y >= rows) return;\n    drawValue = grid[idx(x, y)] ? 0 : 1;\n    grid[idx(x, y)] = drawValue;\n    draw();\n  });\n  canvas.addEventListener('mousemove', e => {\n    if (!drawing) return;\n    const { x, y } = cellFromEvent(e);\n    if (x < 0 || x >= cols || y < 0 || y >= rows) return;\n    grid[idx(x, y)] = drawValue;\n    draw();\n  });\n  window.addEventListener('mouseup', () => drawing = false);\n\n  // --- Buttons ---\n  const toggleBtn = document.getElementById('toggle');\n  toggleBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {\n    running = !running;\n    toggleBtn.textContent = running ? 'Pause' : 'Start';\n  });\n  document.getElementById('step').addEventListener('click', () => { step(); draw(); });\n  document.getElementById('clear').addEventListener('click', () => {\n    grid.fill(0);\n    generation = 0;\n    draw();\n  });\n  document.getElementById('random').addEventListener('click', () => {\n    for (let i = 0; i < grid.length; i++) grid[i] = Math.random() < 0.25 ? 1 : 0;\n    generation = 0;\n    draw();\n  });\n  document.getElementById('speed').addEventListener('input', e => {\n    fps = Number(e.target.value);\n  });\n\n  // Seed with a glider for fun\n  const seed = [[1,0],[2,1],[0,2],[1,2],[2,2]];\n  seed.forEach(([x, y]) => grid[idx(x + 5, y + 5)] = 1);\n\n  draw();\n  requestAnimationFrame(loop);\n})();\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null,"userModified":false},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"88568787-daa6-46b6-bc35-bd5cd8a88c75","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/SteffenPlunder/Documents/Workspace/ping-pong","sessionId":"a3912923-cfb8-4524-a125-b91c3001efb9","version":"2.1.112","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
{"parentUuid":"8a167ed8-21ab-49d7-996b-dcee7cc4c529","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_017rH6rPSyppBVU8H57ja5iH","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`\n- **Toroidal topology**: `(x + dx + cols) % cols` wraps coordinates so the grid edges connect — a glider crossing the right edge reappears on the left. Without this, patterns \"die\" at the boundary.\n- **Decoupling simulation from rendering**: the `loop` uses `requestAnimationFrame` (ties to ~60fps screen refresh) but gates the actual `step()` behind a custom interval (`1000/fps`). This lets the speed slider control simulation rate independently of the render loop, and keeps the UI responsive.\n- **Toggle-on-click drawing**: on `mousedown` we read the cell's current state and invert it, then `mousemove` paints that same value. This is a common UX pattern (used by iOS toggle rows too) — start a drag on a dead cell and everything you touch becomes alive, start on a live cell and you erase.\n`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`\n\nOpen `game-of-life.html` in a browser. A glider is pre-seeded in the corner — hit **Start** to watch it travel diagonally, or click **Random** to fill the board and observe emergent patterns (still lifes, oscillators, occasional gliders)."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2807,"cache_read_input_tokens":24724,"output_tokens":414,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2807,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":414,"cache_read_input_tokens":24724,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2807,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2807},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011C